    <briefdescription>
<para>Evaluates a Chebyshev polynomial series using Clenshaw recurrence. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Evaluates: <verbatim>f(x) = sum_k c_k T_k(x)
</verbatim> where T_k are Chebyshev polynomials of the first kind.</para>
<para>Designed for very large numbers of evaluations with minimal overhead. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
